# C# naming

Match [griddungeon-game](https://github.com/miramocha/griddungeon-game) conventions.

## Conventions

| Kind | Pattern | Example |
|---|---|---|
| Types | PascalCase | `DamageCalculator` |
| Interfaces | `I` + PascalCase | `IMazeGenerator` |
| Private fields | `m_` + camelCase | `m_health` |
| Static fields | `s_` + camelCase | `s_registry` |
| Constants | `k_` + PascalCase | `k_MaxHp` |
| Parameters, locals | camelCase | `targetPosition` |
| Booleans | verb prefix | `isDead`, `hasKey` |
| Methods | verb phrase | `CalculateDamage` |
| Namespaces | PascalCase; mirror folders | `GridDungeon.Core.Simulators` |

## Files

One primary type per file; filename = type name (`DamageCalculator.cs`).

## Do not

- `snake_case` for C# identifiers
- Public fields for DTO state (use properties)
- Abbreviations except loop indices (`i`, `j`)
